game.name: Natalies Winter Treats
game.description:
Natalia is an owner of a beautiful sweet’s shop. Now the winter time has just begun, so she just wants to prepare the delicious treats for the season. Are you able to accept this challenge and help her to please all his customers? She is a very intelligent girl and aware of all the secrets how to cheer up her customers. So, you will also get the support from her while looking forward to get the delicious treats prepared for her customers. Get engaged now and play one of the best free online cooking games for girls! 

In Natalies Winter Treats game, you will have to discover all the epic, rare or common ingredients to prepare finger licking treats. The primary purpose of creating this item is to allow the girl make her sweet’s store successful in the city. Keep finding out all the sweets and collecting money for the new and special ingredients by just making her customers feel happy. For that purpose, all you need to do is to serve all the possible orders of her customers on time. Discover the ingredients and prepare different types of sweets in this brand new cooking game for girls and boys.  

Try out from the delicious hot chocolate, gingerbread men, or cookies. Once you display the items you have created, get ready to serve them to your customers who visit your store to fulfil their various sweet urging needs. After the completion of this cute fun girl cooking game, it’s common to make you feel hungry. Prepare it at your home and make your friends and family surprise by preparing it. Keep playing it until all the ingredients are unlocked!
